{
  "id": "adv_event_2205_01_05",
  "title": "私達なら\n大丈夫",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "（あの日から、お姉ちゃんと私は……明確に変わった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Since that day‚ Onee-chan and I… have clearly changed.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.4940591812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗！　そこでもっと前に！\nもっとお客さんにアピールしよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa! Move further up!\nLet's appeal to the audience more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7,
      "endTime": 10.7078003883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん！　お姉ちゃんも……\nもっと動きを大きくしていいと思う！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah! Onee-chan…\nI think you should make bigger movements!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9,
      "endTime": 16.711247158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "分かったわ。……ふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. …Hehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9,
      "endTime": 19.666031789799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8666666667,
      "endTime": 21.0803628366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "（譲り合っていたこれまでとは真逆の……）\n（どちらがもっと輝けるかを競う日々）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Completely opposite to what we've been doing so far…)\n(Competing every day to see who can shine more…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2666666667,
      "endTime": 27.708367411300003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "（お互いに思ったことは全部言う。今までなら、関係が）\n（壊れちゃうのを怖がってとても出来なかったけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We say everything we think to each other. In the past‚ our relationship…)\n(was fragile‚ and I was too scared to do that…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9,
      "endTime": 37.4705898284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "（今はそんなやりとりが、楽しくてしょうがなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But now‚ I find such exchanges enjoyable and exciting.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6666666667,
      "endTime": 42.481405703300005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "サビだけど、その手前までは私の出番が多めでしょ？\nだからここは千紗をもっと前に出した方がいいかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The chorus‚ but before that‚ I have more lines‚ right?\nSo‚ maybe it's better to put Chisa more forward here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7666666667,
      "endTime": 54.689161364300006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "でも……この部分で私がまるまる前に出ちゃうと\n私の印象ばっかり強くならないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… if I take the lead completely in this part…\nWon't the focus be too much on me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9,
      "endTime": 63.275328826899994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "それだと……私の方が人気出ちゃうよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then… I might become more popular‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4666666667,
      "endTime": 68.2826984088,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2377.4033469000033
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "……言ってくれるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's nice of you to say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4666666667,
      "endTime": 70.45573701069999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ケ、ケンカはだめだよ！\n二人とも、一体どうしちゃったの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "F-Fighting is not good!\nWhat happened to both of you?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6666666667,
      "endTime": 75.1228346507,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……そう見えても不思議じゃないですよね\nごめんなさい、渚ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I guess it's not surprising that it looks that way.\nI'm sorry‚ Nagisa-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3333333333,
      "endTime": 82.0429931958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "真剣に話し合ってるけど……\nケンカはしてないから。大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're having a serious discussion…\nBut we're not fighting. Don't worry‚ we're fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2333333333,
      "endTime": 87.3875737507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、こんな風に話し合えるのが新鮮で……\n楽しくて仕方ないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In fact‚ being able to have discussions like this…\nIt's refreshing and… I can't help but find it fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6,
      "endTime": 93.7845219612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1233622234,
      "endTime": 96.6333622615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "……二人とも、とっても変わったね\nもちろんいい意味で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Both of you have changed a lot.\nIn a good way‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8233622234,
      "endTime": 102.15962092090001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "決勝、楽しみにしてるね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm looking forward to the finals!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.660383606,
      "endTime": 104.99702758789999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ユニットバトル決勝当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of Team Battle Finals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9608144124,
      "endTime": 108.0808144649,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2279.716491800002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2279.716491800002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.1456338008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　沙季ちゃんと千紗ちゃん！　応援に来たよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! Saiki-chan and Chisa-chan! We came to cheer you on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2341272991,
      "endTime": 113.046462838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.2341272991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "皆さん……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2341272991,
      "endTime": 116.1748755615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.3674606324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと一生懸命歌を届けるから、観ててね……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll do our best to deliver a heartfelt performance‚ so please watch us…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3674606324,
      "endTime": 121.5878121377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.1026713054
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "頑張ってね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good luck!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1026713054,
      "endTime": 123.1826712768,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 533.4548950000055
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 967.8421020000059
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9635762533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか……沙季ちゃんも千紗ちゃんも\n顔つきが違う気がする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Somehow… Saiki-chan and Chisa-chan's\nfacial expressions seem different…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.9635762533,
      "endTime": 130.3134853681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、自信満々って感じだったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ they seem full of confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4969095867,
      "endTime": 133.9691543739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.1635762533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_05-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃん、千紗ちゃん……楽しみにしてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saiki-chan‚ Chisa-chan… I'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
